post1:
After all this time , the 5 of us still have our meet ups!  We just carry on chatting as though  we met yesterday and it's not just a yearly event. Great friends,  really lucky to be still in touch .
Luckily we're all in Good health... apart from a few old age creaks and cracks.
Already planned next year venue.

Glad you're my husband...
Happy birthday xxxx  and many more  to come xxxx
